                  <p class="text-secondary-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Launched our MVP with 50 beta customers. Raised $2M in seed funding from top-tier VCs to accelerate development and hiring.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- 2023 -->
            <div class="relative flex items-center animate-on-scroll">
              <div class="absolute left-8 w-4 h-4 bg-green-600 rounded-full transform -translate-x-1/2 border-4 border-white shadow-lg"></div>
              <div class="ml-20">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-secondary-200 p-6 shadow-sm">
                  <div class="text-sm text-green-600 font-semibold mb-2">2023</div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary-900 mb-3">Rapid Growth</h3>
                  <p class="text-secondary-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Reached 1,000+ customers and launched 200+ integrations. Expanded team to 25 people across engineering, product, and customer success.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- 2024 -->
            <div class="relative flex items-center animate-on-scroll">
              <div class="absolute left-8 w-4 h-4 bg-blue-600 rounded-full transform -translate-x-1/2 border-4 border-white shadow-lg"></div>
              <div class="ml-20">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-secondary-200 p-6 shadow-sm">
                  <div class="text-sm text-blue-600 font-semibold mb-2">2024</div>
                  <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-secondary-900 mb-3">Series A & AI Integration</h3>
                  <p class="text-secondary-600 leading-relaxed">
                    Closed $15M Series A round. Launched AI-powered workflow optimization and advanced analytics. Achieved SOC 2 compliance.
                  </p>
                </div>
              </div>
            </div>
            
            <!-- 2025 -->
            <div class="relative flex items-center animate-on-scroll">
              <div class="absolute left-8 w-4 h-4 bg-purple-600 rounded-full transform -translate-x-1/2 border-4 border-white shadow-lg"></div>
              <div class="ml-20">
                <div class="bg-white rounded-lg border border-secondary-200 p-6 shadow-sm">
